<emphasis id="6EDEBBFDC33B7C52AF7E17224244E455" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G.B. Hinton et al</emphasis>
. 8590 (K, GH); ibid., 
<normalizedToken id="DFE0E81C9D63B84993208C2E0A353A34" originalValue="Rincón">Rincon</normalizedToken>
del Carmen, 
<emphasis id="CA09D675AAD91FC6DECC418268B161C2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">G.B. Hinton et al</emphasis>
